- **This repository’s conventions are codified as individual contractual rules**
  - Treat every referenced rule as binding.
  - When two rules appear to conflict, follow the stricter requirement and do not introduce new behavior without explicit user instruction.

- **Core repository-wide constraints (existing enforced rules)**
  - **No file deletion without explicit user confirmation**: [no-file-deletion.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/no-file-deletion.mdc)
  - **No fallbacks unless explicitly requested**: [fallbacks.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/fallbacks.mdc)
  - **No `text-muted`, no `form-text`, no `opacity-*` on text**: [text-muted-dark-background.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/text-muted-dark-background.mdc)
  - **Bootstrap is primary; custom CSS enhances only**: [Bootstrap.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/Bootstrap.mdc)
  - **External CSS only**: [css_organization.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/css_organization.mdc)
  - **External JavaScript only**: [javascript_organization.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/javascript_organization.mdc)

